      "final_prompt": {
        "prompt": "Create a 3:4 vertical 3x3 grid poster for Xiaohongshu (Little Red Book), designed as 9 separate cards that can be cleanly sliced into individual posts.\n\nStyle/medium: Clean editorial design with soft illustration accents, professional social media aesthetic, ins-style wellness visual language\nComposition: 3 columns × 3 rows grid layout with clear borders/gutters between each cell, each cell centered and self-contained, generous white space, no text crossing grid lines\nSubject: Sleep wellness tips for women, featuring soft pillows, moons, stars, warm milk, aromatherapy, books, eye masks, curtains, beds\nScene/backdrop: Cream white and oat beige background throughout all 9 cells, unified gentle atmosphere\nLighting/mood: Soft diffused warm light, cozy and healing bedtime mood\nColor palette: Cream white, light beige, pale oat, soft caramel as base; dark brown for text; warm yellow accents for lamps; minimal high-contrast elements\nMaterials/textures: Matte paper-like surfaces, soft fabric textures for pillows and bedding, subtle grain for warmth\nText (verbatim): \"让你倒头就睡的8个 tips\", \"失眠党、熬夜党一定要收藏\", \"1. 睡前1小时别玩手机\", \"蓝光会让大脑更清醒，越刷越睡不着。\", \"2. 睡前把灯光调暗\", \"暖光环境能帮助身体进入\"准备睡觉\"的状态。\", \"3. 房间温度别太高\", \"稍微凉一点，更容易快速入睡。\", \"4. 晚上别喝浓茶咖啡\", \"咖啡因会延迟困意，让你躺很久还睡不着。\", \"5. 睡前洗个热水澡\", \"能让身体放松下来，入睡速度更快。\", \"6. 脑子停不下来就写下来\", \"把烦心事和待办清单写下，大脑会更容易放松。\", \"7. 固定上床时间\", \"每天差不多时间睡，生物钟会越来越稳定。\", \"8. 试试深呼吸放松法\", \"吸气4秒，停4秒，呼气6秒，慢慢就有困意了。\", \"收藏这组，今晚试试看\"\nConstraints: All 9 cells must be visually cohesive when viewed as one poster; each cell must work as standalone Xiaohongshu cover; grid lines must be precise for clean slicing; all text in Chinese only; large readable typography; no text near cut lines\nAvoid: Cheap marketing aesthetic, excessive decoration, cluttered layout, garish colors, small unreadable text, English text, misaligned grid, text crossing cell boundaries, watermark, 8K stuffer words",
