      "final_prompt": {
        "prompt": "Create an original, non-infringing travel infographic for a 4-day 3-night Hangzhou itinerary, designed as a tri-fold brochure with famous landmarks floating on card stock over a real Hangzhou map background.\n\nStyle/medium: travel infographic / tri-fold brochure design, editorial layout with illustrated landmark icons, clean typography, flat vector style with subtle depth shadows\nComposition: three-panel tri-fold layout, top-down map view as base layer, landmark illustrations floating above with soft drop shadows, clear day-by-day sections with route lines connecting attractions\nSubject: Hangzhou 4-day itinerary with illustrated landmarks — 断桥残雪 (Broken Bridge), 雷峰塔 (Leifeng Pagoda), 灵隐寺 (Lingyin Temple), 法喜寺 (Fayu Temple), 九溪烟树 (Nine Creeks), 龙井村 (Longjing Village), 拱宸桥 (Gongchen Bridge), 西溪湿地 (Xixi Wetland)\nScene/backdrop: stylized real Hangzhou city map as background base layer, card stock texture visible at edges, clean white/ivory paper surface with subtle grain\nLighting/mood: soft even studio lighting, professional product photography feel, inviting and organized travel guide aesthetic\nColor palette: soft jade green and lake blue as primary (西湖 water tones), warm terracotta accents for landmarks, cream/off-white for paper, black for typography\nText (verbatim): \"第一天：西湖经典游，打卡教科书里的江南\", \"断桥残雪→白堤→孤山→曲院风荷→苏堤春晓→花港观鱼→雷峰塔→柳浪闻莺\", \"第二天：禅意杭州，穿越千年宋韵\", \"灵隐寺→飞来峰造像→法喜寺→宋城\", \"第三天：九溪烟树徒步，做一日茶山散人\", \"九溪十八涧→龙井村→十里琅珰→云栖竹径\", \"第四天：文艺收官，解锁杭州AB面\", \"拱宸桥→桥西历史街区→小河直街→大兜路香积寺\", \"周家村→深潭口→氦气球俯瞰湿地\"\nMaterials/textures: matte card stock paper texture, subtle embossed effect on landmark icons, clean vector lines for map, slight paper fiber visible\nConstraints: all text must be legible at print size; landmark icons must be recognizable silhouettes; map must suggest real Hangzhou geography without being navigation-accurate\nAvoid: photorealistic 3D render, cluttered layout, unreadable small text, generic stock travel icons, watermark, 8K stuffer words",
